  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nWe've added support for hardhat-etherscan on harmony and created a small patch to support the harmony network (change in two files, chainconfig.ts and types.ts). I would like to push this as a PR as a lot of developers have been asking for hardhat-etherscan support to make contract verification much easier on the harmony network.\r\n\r\nBelow are some details on what has been done so far:\r\nDocumentation: [Verifying proxies using hardhat and harmony](https://victa-kwok-wai-phu.gitbook.io/harmony-contract-verification-service/verifying-proxy-contracts/transparent-proxies)\r\nFork: [hardhat with harmony](https://github.com/victaphu/hardhat/tree/master)\r\n\r\nIf this is acceptable I can use this issue to push a PR into your repository.\r\n\r\nThanks!\r\n\r\nVicta\r\n\r\n",
